<h2 id="lightspeed">Lightspeed Restaurant</h2>

Lightspeed Restaurant is a cloud-based POS with strong reporting and inventory features. It's particularly good for restaurants with complex menus, wine lists, or ingredient-level inventory tracking.

<h3>Strengths:</h3>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Advanced inventory</strong> -- ingredient-level tracking, recipe costing, waste management</li>
  <li><strong>Floor plan management</strong> -- visual table layout with section assignments</li>
  <li><strong>Reporting depth</strong> -- labor, menu engineering, and inventory reports exceed Toast and Square</li>
  <li><strong>Integration ecosystem</strong> -- 200+ partners including major delivery and accounting platforms</li>
</ul>

<h3>Limitations:</h3>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Not restaurant-exclusive</strong> -- shared platform with retail, which shows in some workflows</li>
  <li><strong>Hardware is generic</strong> -- iPad-based, not restaurant-grade</li>
  <li><strong>Pricing is opaque</strong> -- requires consultation for multi-location quotes</li>
  <li><strong>KDS is add-on</strong> -- not included in base plans</li>
</ul>

