<h2 id="verdict">Final Recommendation</h2>

<div class="verdict-box">
  <h3>The Restaurant POS Decision</h3>
  <p><strong>Full-service restaurants (3+ locations):</strong> Toast. The restaurant-grade hardware, native KDS, and multi-location management are purpose-built for this use case.<br/><br/>
  <strong>Fast-casual / counter-service (any size):</strong> Square for Restaurants. Lower commitment, excellent free tier, and the Square ecosystem covers most needs.<br/><br/>
  <strong>Complex menus / ingredient tracking:</strong> Lightspeed Restaurant. Best inventory and reporting for restaurants that need ingredient-level management.<br/><br/>
  <strong>Avoid:</strong> Clover for multi-location. The reseller model creates operational inconsistency that compounds across locations.</p>
</div>

